{"tid":569592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴個apps真係好撚廢","createTime":"2018-02-22T23:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T00:27:24.000Z","uid":60709,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca28cbd0e82429160281d515cf535062b5efa1a","tid":569592,"uid":60709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T23:58:36.000Z","msg":"平時架車都好飄忽架啦，一時搭7黎一時搭8黎，見個apps話仲有5分鐘，拿拿聲衝去巴士站等車<br />\n我見個站上面都話下架車仲有幾分鐘，心諗冇死啦今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屌佢老母等左10幾分鐘都唔見有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來佢個仲有5分鐘係報緊上一架車，姐係個報時根本就一早已經delay左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面排隊d人都發覺唔對路唔再等，最後全部走哂去搭西鐵<br />\n屌你老母九巴檢討下啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d5d0a4783c9abd4252180d2b4cd1894160e4e9","tid":569592,"uid":164457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:01:50.000Z","msg":"屌我前一分鐘先經歷完 成廿分鐘先一班 不過我好啲等到下一架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1015d97e208936164ffa8d3fe5d684b103234f","tid":569592,"uid":45582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:05:01.000Z","msg":"公司對面係巴士站。<br />\n試過佢預計5:58到站,我預早少少放工5:55到樓下 , 一出lift就見架巴士啱啱由站開走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8881bfd8410893bf87ea1f6faf0b4db7458fd7","tid":569592,"uid":2857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:10:06.000Z","msg":"個app一開<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，全版廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c24d99fef8057a06c5dceb5908fb5effb5c351","tid":569592,"uid":153480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"如果睇兩間公司合辦嘅巴士路線，要計番兩個班次中間仲有一架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7adf349c594058e7835450cbb80d40d80a383f7","tid":569592,"uid":2333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:13:18.000Z","msg":"算幾準  8成"},{"pid":"790ef2b982c36a2838e48788332cc34779981131","tid":569592,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:15:05.000Z","msg":"係架，屌琴日我係九龍灣落車，個eta話我部車仲係新蒲崗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會數錯，我坐特別線尾二車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fc48ea07f82afd84b676d43d7e2dfa6ccf05e3","tid":569592,"uid":146213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c24d99fef8057a06c5dceb5908fb5effb5c351","tid":569592,"uid":153480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"如果睇兩間公司合辦嘅巴士路線，要計番兩個班次中間仲有一架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:27:24.000Z","msg":"城巴/新巴時段班次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}